{"tid":1488713,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人加油","createTime":"2019-08-19T16:35:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T18:03:29.000Z","uid":309870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"45ef5cd767abf64319d063f3b590db333707472d","tid":1488713,"uid":309870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:35:17.000Z","msg":"我係一個啱啱上u嘅學生<br />\n冇去到ocamp 冇參加u嘅活動<br />\n又冇錢去支援買物資 因為之前傷左而家有傷口 同唔到大家一齊去發夢<br />\n不過想講嘅係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人加油</span><br />\n無論發生咩事都好!  大家都要團結啊<br />\n唔好比人分化 要比心機繼續堅持落去<br />\n我咁樣講好似好廢<br />\n不過我都好想講 就算出唔到黎 <br />\n精神上同社交平台上嘅文宣都會繼續幫手!<br />\n最後大家唔好比人影響到我地嘅五大訴求啊"},{"pid":"9f186a96e135c3b398d2f2b54a71d45ead573f10","tid":1488713,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:37:00.000Z","msg":"（整合） 818之後仲有行動㗎我地！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1487938\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1487938</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"780bdd618fa57143828117ca5c493842fd902fbd","tid":1488713,"uid":107898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:40:04.000Z","msg":"多謝您<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果行動不便就做鍵戰<br />\n如果落到樓既,落樓宣傳下<br />\n兄弟爬山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81d675358426e247842feb8a88881956ef81d22c","tid":1488713,"uid":309870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"780bdd618fa57143828117ca5c493842fd902fbd","tid":1488713,"uid":107898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:40:04.000Z","msg":"多謝您<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果行動不便就做鍵戰<br />\n如果落到樓既,落樓宣傳下<br />\n兄弟爬山<im